song_lyrics: Māre āvyo alaukik dāv re, koī mune shu karashe;
Māthā sāṭe varyā me to māv re... Koī° 1
Have baḷe chhe jagmā balāy re... Koī°
Men to bheṭyā chhe Bhūdhar rāy re... Koī° 2
Ati ānand thayo chhe māre ang re... Koī°
Thaī jagmā alaukik jīt re... Koī°
Lāgī pūraṇ salūṇā sāthe prīt re... Koī° 4
Māre vhāle dīdhu chhe mane mān re... Koī°
Mane kīdhī sohāgaṇ kahān re... Koī° 5
Have thayo sansārīḍo zer re... Koī°
Brahmānandne vā’lejī kīdhī maher re... Koī° 6
title: Māre āvyo alaukik dāv re
